Type: Form
Name: Missile
Initial DC: +1
Addt'l DC: +0
DC Bonus: N/A
Description: A [Form]Missile Spell appears as a fist-sized bolt of energy, which flies from one or both hands. When triggered, the effect emenates from the bolt in a roughly 1 meter diameter blast. The spell is triggered on contact with any solid or liquid, except the caster's hands. The Spell is an Attack, Distance 3-1,  Interval 1s, 1.5-Handed, X Min STR, Thrown.
